so today, we've done 2 more things in combine. won't tell here. check IDEAL TIME TABLE or README for that. heres the context code:


import Combine

var bag = Set<AnyCancellable>()

let tap = PassthroughSubject<Void, Never>()
let count = CurrentValueSubject<Int, Never>(0)

count
    .sink { print("Count:", $0) }
    .store(in: &bag)

tap
    .sink {
        count.send(count.value + 1)
    }
    .store(in: &bag)

// Simulate events
tap.send()
tap.send()
tap.send()
count.send(10)
tap.send()